{"tid":2457571,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人鍾意女裝潛入大小姐學園類作品","createTime":"2021-03-22T17:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T22:10:35.000Z","uid":174949,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"657838c388ea1c4cc7cc5da81ba65f924a59b30a","tid":2457571,"uid":174949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T17:48:23.000Z","msg":"本身好就已經好鍾意大小姐學園作品<br />\n例如瑪莉亞的凝望, 驚爆草莓, flowers<br />\n每日都講貴安, 姐姐大人, 同祈禱<br />\n覺得佢地好高貴優雅, 好歐式風格<br />\n而女裝潛入類作品係用男人視覺去enjoy女校生活, 令我更加有代入感<br />\n大小姐學園對於男人嚟講係未知嘅世界, 同轉生異世界一樣<br />\n見到男主比女同學更有女人味, 被低年級學生仰慕, 同時要keep住自己身為男性嘅秘密<br />\n都會想笑同有優越感<br />\n<br />\n我最鍾意嘅作品係少女愛上姐姐2<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.inside-games.jp/imgs/zoom/184819.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inside-games.jp%2Fimgs%2Fzoom%2F184819.jpg&h=aa1baf97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想做高貴大小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08af5746febb3e564774a73d6681b9471829638","tid":2457571,"uid":184233,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T17:49:33.000Z","msg":"已射<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5ef83a8087bd293e035dc4a3aa0331ffa96723","tid":2457571,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T18:00:57.000Z","msg":"好耐以前玩過花與少女的祝福<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d37cee514e2716b59d0919cbb288f3d4586d492","tid":2457571,"uid":174949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b08af5746febb3e564774a73d6681b9471829638","tid":2457571,"uid":184233,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T17:49:33.000Z","msg":"已射<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T18:07:59.000Z","msg":"嘛~果然是男孩子呢~"},{"pid":"356cf7bd33b7b4c16d69a03a6ab8bf02f7e66b25","tid